{"tid":2412106,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"三十秒科學–Royal Purple","createTime":"2021-02-17T23:32:39.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-19T05:13:00.000Z","uid":38861,"like":34,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"b16a61741fe0b140240b7bcbe2f99b97d92347f2","tid":2412106,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T23:32:39.000Z","msg":"紫色可以是從紅加藍而成，這是無容置疑。<br />\n但古時候的人又是從甚麼途徑獲取紫色顏料呢?<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XMLhbTC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXMLhbTC.jpg&h=398d1c93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n(圖2）紫色顏料其中的一道渠道，就是從骨螺而來。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UqCn7rZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUqCn7rZ.png&h=392af915&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n顏色的來源當然並非來自骨螺外部，而是來自內部一道名為鰓下腺(Hypobranchial gland)的器官。<br />\n<br />\n提取過程相當複雜，而且顏色最終的光澤將取決於骨螺的新鮮度，平均來說每隻骨螺最終只可提取得到約0.9克的顏料。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（圖3）從以色列南部找出屬於約3000年前(鐵器時代)的紫色羊毛纖維中，找到骨螺鰓下腺器官內含的6-monobromoindigotin和6,6-dibromoindigotin的化學物質，進一步引證從骨螺提取紫色顏料的證據。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/woOq5dK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwoOq5dK.png&h=08fb48f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據稱，從骨螺而來的紫色染料一律將被命名為True Purple或是Royal Purple，對比其他來自植物或礦物得來的紫色染料，較不容易會褪色。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n延伸閱讀:深入淺出&ndash;以化學角度審視吶喊名畫<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2204104\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2204104</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果想我快啲出文的話，請入去Penana網站科普專欄&ndash;薯不揀單俾一個like以及Bookmark，這對我非常之重要。<br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fstory%2F66244%2F%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%25B0%2588%25E6%25AC%2584-%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258F%2580%25E5%2596%25AE%2Ftoc&d=3nH4Hj8OzEJ%2Fsn4LiTBSOlJiVKGJ8LWvq%2BeQg4NrPGo%3D&h=75aa34fc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc</a><br />\n<br />\n同時亦可以在Penana網站裡按「買一嚿/半嚿薯仔」，以課金的方式推動我繼續搜羅資料寫文，多謝。<br />\n<br />\nLink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fuser%2F27349%2F%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25BB%2594%25E8%2581%259E%25E8%258C%25B1%25E8%258E%2589%2Fportfolio&d=3nH4Hj8OzEJ%2Fsn4LiTBSOlJiVKGJ8LWvq%2BeQg4NrPGo%3D&h=31ae7585\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n除非Facebook及IG重開侵侵的account，否則我的IG將不會再作更新，只會寄居本土LIHKG及Penana。<br />\n<br />\nRef1:<a href=\"https://journals.plos.org/plosone/article?id=10.1371/journal.pone.0245897#pone.0245897.ref007\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fjournals.plos.org%2Fplosone%2Farticle%3Fid%3D10.1371%2Fjournal.pone.0245897%23pone.0245897.ref007&d=3nH4Hj8OzEJ%2Fsn4LiTBSOlJiVKGJ8LWvq%2BeQg4NrPGo%3D&h=3161edea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://journals.plos.org/plosone/article?id=10.1371/journal.pone.0245897#pone.0245897.ref007</a><br />\nRef2:<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC6562550/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC6562550%2F&d=3nH4Hj8OzEJ%2Fsn4LiTBSOlJiVKGJ8LWvq%2BeQg4NrPGo%3D&h=629f7470\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC6562550/</a>"},{"pid":"9f01667d51b9b7564fa08d8ba67f8cc9b25e8b89","tid":2412106,"uid":135554,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T23:36:34.000Z","msg":"咁點解3000年前嘅人會知道可以喺骨螺提取到紫色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"759c07e5f8dfcd6a93b5922dc6ef8276fbd46a45","tid":